    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Yungasacris species. A, G–H. Y. multa. Male habitus, cerci in dorsal and lateral view respectively. B–C. Y. grata grata cerci in dorsal and lateral view. D. Y. grata rara cerci in lateral view. E–F. Y. peruviana cerci in dorsal and lateral view respectively. (Figs. B–F. after Rehn, 1950, Figs. D, G–H. after Cadena-Castañeda & Gorochov, 2013)." ;
